Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_TONY>
I came here to find goods for import, but this
town doesn't have a particularly good selection
just yet.

<NAME_MOB_TONY>
Every now and again, I find a real gem here.
That's why I keep coming back.

<NAME_MOB_TONY>
Man, I sure made out like a bandit today! What a
haul!

<NAME_MOB_TONY>
I can find products from lots of other foreign
countries here. It's really convenient!

<NAME_MOB_TONY>
I'm a trader. And this is my game. This...is
where I belong. And where I feel most at home.

<NAME_MOB_TONY>
I'm pretty new to this business, so I've still got a
lot to learn. But I'm learning! Oh, how I am
learning!
